  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要做一个关于子图间距配置的示例图，用来展示nodeSpacing和rankSpacing的效果。整体布局从左到右，包含两个子图X和Y，它们之间要有连接关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "子图X",
        "子图Y",
        "nodeSpacing",
        "rankSpacing",
        "LR方向"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以主流程图是LR方向，X和Y作为两个子图并排。每个子图内部也是LR方向吗？还有X和Y之间是单向连接还是双向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "主流程图方向",
        "子图内部方向",
        "X-Y连接"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，子图X和Y内部都是LR方向。X指向Y，单向连接。X里面放A和C两个节点，Y里面放B和D。标题就叫\"Subgraph nodeSpacing and rankSpacing example\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "子图X",
        "A",
        "C",
        "子图Y",
        "B",
        "D",
        "X→Y连接",
        "标题"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来配置一下。config里面把flowchart的nodeSpacing和rankSpacing都设为1，这样间距会比较紧凑。子图X包含A和C，子图Y包含B和D，都用LR方向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "config.flowchart.nodeSpacing",
        "config.flowchart.rankSpacing",
        "子图X",
        "子图Y"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，X和Y之间的连接方式，我说的是X指向Y，这个在Mermaid里直接写\"X -- Y\"可以吗？还是需要用箭头？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "X-Y连接",
        "连接符号"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "用\"X -- Y\"是可以的，Mermaid会解析为连接。不过严格来说，如果强调方向性，用\"X -- Y\"更明确。但按照你的要求，保持\"--\"也没问题，flowchart LR的上下文会让方向清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "X-Y连接",
        "连接符号"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那就保持\"--\"吧，这样更简洁。另外确认一下节点顺序：X里面是A在上、C在下，Y里面是B在上、D在下，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "C",
        "B",
        "D",
        "节点顺序"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
